31/01/2005
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Wrapping up a two-day visit to Turkey on Saturday (29 January), Bulgarian Foreign Minister Solomon Passy urged the accelerated opening of a new border crossing with Turkey, near the Rezovska River. 
The new crossing would likely function only during the summer tourist season. 
(Turks.US - 30/01/05; Bulgarian Foreign Ministry Web site, BNR - 29/01/05)
